{
  "stem": "9963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what I did, actually, in that camp, where I bribed the foremen, they allowed me to go away from work and go to farmers to work during the day, what I can get food from the farmers, you know.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In a Saturday, with the-- I would-- took that food, took it home for my parents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because in the city, it was very hard to get food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the bread-- you had to stay in a line.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And many times you came close already to get the bread and they were out, and didn't got it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You had to wait for another day where they come another shipment what they will bake.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was very hard for my parents, my sister-- you know, at home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you see, in that camp, I was able to bribe the foremen, go to work at the-- you know-- to the farmers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And not for money-- just for to give me flour, give me beans, give me the whatever I could get from them for my work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Saturday I had a full sack of food-- I brought it home for my parents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How far away from your town was this camp?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, with the street, to go was about 35 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I went to the mountains what I mentioned before, when I found a way through the mountains to go home, I saved about 50% of-- in other words, it was about 15 to 17 kilometers through the mountains.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a tough road.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, it wasn't-- I had to climb.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to go down and up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I saved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It took me about three, four hours to walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, our house was a brand new home.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
